{{Expand Galician|date=September 2017}} {{Use dmy dates|date=September 2017}} {{infobox writer | name = Luís Pimentel | image = Luis Pimentel.jpg | imagesize = 220px | alt = | caption = | pseudonym = | birth_name = {{Nowrap|Luís Vázquez Fernández-Pimentel}} | birth_date = 18 December 1895 | birth_place = [[Lugo]], Galicia | death_date = {{death date and age|df=yes|1958|02|13|1895|12|18}} | death_place = [[Lugo]], Galicia | resting_place = | occupation = Physician | language = [[Spanish language|Spanish]] and [[Galician language|Galician]] | education = Medicine | alma_mater = {{Nowrap|[[University of Santiago de Compostela]]}} | period = | genre = | subject = | movement = | notableworks = | spouse = Pilar Cayón Fernández | partner = | children = One | relatives = | awards = | signature = Luis V. F. Pimentel, sinatura, detalle.jpg | signature_alt = signature detail | portaldisp = }} '''Luís Vázquez Fernández-Pimentel''' (b. [[Lugo]], 18 December 1895 – d. Lugo, 13 February 1958) was a [[Galician people|Galician]] poet.
[[Galician Literature Day]] is dedicated to him in 1990.<ref>[http://academia.gal/figuras-homenaxeadas/-/journal_content/56_INSTANCE_8klA/10157/16111 ''Día das Letras Galegas''] [[Royal Galician Academy]].</ref>
